---
import { FeaturedSVG } from '../config'
import house from '/src/assets/svg/undraw/house.jpg';
---

<div class='relative overflow-hidden bg-white dark:bg-gray-900'>
  <div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl'>
    <div
      class='relative z-10 bg-white pb-8 dark:bg-gray-900 sm:pb-16 md:pb-20 lg:w-full lg:max-w-2xl lg:pb-28 xl:pb-32'
    >
      <svg
        class='absolute inset-y-0 right-0 hidden h-full w-48 translate-x-1/2 transform text-white dark:text-gray-900 lg:block'
        fill='currentColor'
        viewBox='0 0 100 100'
        preserveAspectRatio='none'
        aria-hidden='true'
      >
        <polygon points='50,0 100,0 50,100 0,100'></polygon>
      </svg>
      <main
        class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 pt-10 sm:px-6 sm:pt-12 md:pt-16 lg:px-8 lg:pt-20 xl:pt-28'
      >
        <div class='text-center sm:text-left'>
          <h1
            class='text-left text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl'
          >
            <span class='block xl:inline'></span>{' '}
            <br>
            <span class='text-black-700 dark:text-black-300 block xl:inline'
              >Welcome to Futurx - Your Gateway to Global Education</span
            >
          </h1>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mx-auto sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0'
          >
            Unlock endless opportunities for your future by pursuing higher education abroad.
          </p>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mx-auto sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0'
          >
            Whether you're aiming for a bachelor's, master's, or PhD, Futurx provides everything you
            need to start your journey: education loans, accommodation, visa guidance, forex
            solutions, expert advice, and much more.
          </p>
          <p
            class='mt-3 text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 sm:mx-auto sm:mt-5 sm:max-w-xl sm:text-lg md:mt-5 md:text-xl lg:mx-0'
          >
            Stay informed with our expert articles, tips, and success stories from students who have
            embarked on their global education journeys.
          </p>
          <div class='mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start'>
            <div class='rounded-md shadow'>
              <a
                href='/about'
                class='flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-gray-100 px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-gray-800 hover:bg-pink-600 dark:bg-gray-300 dark:text-black dark:hover:bg-pink-300 md:px-10 md:py-4 md:text-lg'
              >
                About
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class='mt-3 sm:ml-3 sm:mt-0'>
              <a
                href='/blog'
                class='flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-gray-600 px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white-800 hover:bg-gray-200 dark:bg-purple-900 dark:text-purple-100 dark:hover:bg-pink-900 md:px-10 md:py-4 md:text-lg'
              >
                Blog
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-500 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2'>
    <img
    class='-img h-56 w-full object-cover sm:h-72 md:h-96 lg:h-full lg:w-full'
    src={house.src}
    alt='featured'
  />
  
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .logo-img {
    width: 1200px; /* Adjust the size as needed */
  }
</style>
